But I kept saying, "What do you know about farming?" "Sir, I know nothing, but I can learn."  And my staff is saying, "Oh, hire him, hes perfect." I said, "But he doesnt know anything." And then another came in and he had some other talent, but farming wasnt one of them. And a third one came in and I said, "Let me ask you…" -- this guy really seemed to be a total novice -- "Have you ever been to a farm?" "No, sir.
