Massive water. And then we get it from the other side, with essentially a tornado. That was massively wide. That was the worlds biggest tornado. Ive never seen anything like it. You go down to the shore; we saw houses where the foundations were actually ripped out of the ground. I mean, there was nothing.
But the foundations were gone. They werent even left. It was total devastation.
